text: Jeanette James is a former Trinidadian woman cricketer who has played for Trinidad and Tobago in 4 WODIs. She made her Women's One Day International debut against Australia in a group stage match during the 1973 Women's Cricket World Cup. == References == == External links == * * Category:Date of birth missing Category:Possibly living people Category:Trinidad and Tobago women cricketers Category:West Indian women cricketers Category:1946 births
